---
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import mbbsImg from "@assets/img/mbbs.jpg";
import GeorgiaImg from "@assets/img/Georgia3.jpg";
---

<section>
  <div class="united-stats-area pt-120">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-6">
            <Image src={GeorgiaImg} alt="Australia Image" width="600" />
          </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="united-states">
            <style>
              .text-center {
                text-align: center !important;
              }

              .tab-pane {
                display: none;
              }
              .tab-pane.active {
                display: block;
              }
              .nav-tabs {
                flex-direction: column;
              }
              .nav-tabs .nav-link {
                border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
                border-radius: 0.25rem;
                margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
              }
              .nav-tabs .nav-link.active {
                background-color: #007bff;
                color: white;
              }
            </style>

            <h2 class="united-states__title mb-15">ADVANTAGES MBBS IN GEORGIA</h2>

           <p>
            Pursuing an MBBS in Georgia offers numerous advantages that make it an
             attractive option for aspiring medical students. Georgia is home to several
              top-ranked medical universities recognized by international bodies such as the WHO and UNESCO, 
            ensuring that students receive a high standard of education. 
           </p>
            <p>
                The affordability of tuition fees, compared to many Western countries, 
                makes it a cost-effective choice without compromising on quality.
                 Additionally, the availability of English-medium programs eliminates language barriers, making it accessible to a global student population. Students benefit from extensive clinical exposure, gaining practical
                 experience in well-equipped hospitals and medical centers.
            </p>

            <p>
                Furthermore, the degrees awarded by Georgian universities are globally recognized, allowing graduates to pursue medical careers in various countries, including the US and Europe. Overall, studying MBBS in Georgia provides a blend of high-quality education, international recognition, and an enriching cultural experience.
            </p>

            
          </div>
         
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
